high_descs: Turn right and take three steps and then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the candle that is sitting behind another candle.
Turn right for two steps, turn right for six steps and stop.
Open the drawer on the cabinet under the sink, put the candle in the back left of the drawer and then close it.
Turn left for one step, turn right for two steps and stop at the sink.
Pick up the candle to the right of the sink.
Turn around and take two steps, turn left and take one step then turn left again and stop.
Open the drawer on the cabinet under the sink, set the candle down to the right of the existing candle and then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in the drawer under the sink.
